  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what happened is these two cousins of ours, they did come and they made it to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were hiding in Budapest, because they had no paper, you know, legally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those days, already, when you get on a train, you had to show your paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From one town to another, if I took the train, which I did, to [INAUDIBLE], I had to have, like, a little passport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course they knew you were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You had-- when you-- when they looked for the ticket, and you purchased the ticket, you had to show that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When the conductor came on the train, you had to show it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they know you were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you were always, always kind of scary and shy away, and just behave very, very quietly, that they shouldn't even notice you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So these two cousin of ours escaped to Hungary, were for a while in Budapest, and then they emigrated to-- they wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time was Israel Palestine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they did go, and evidently, the history says-- I mean, they really found out the date, that they took that ship-- you know, the illegal ship, which the British confiscated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they died on the ship or they died in a camp there, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they never made it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] that was it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
